The '''INS ''Intimidator''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. It was sent to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ananuru]] when the research details for a secret Imperial [[RNA brainwashing virus]] appeared for auction on the ''[[Ananuru Express]]''. When [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] agent [[Secesh Trant]] attempted to steal the [[Data-tape/Legends|datatape]] at the auction, she threatened everyone there that the forces of the INS ''Intimidator'' were close by if they caused any trouble.

